From a1ef973d4431b059867a6ab637795ca68d6cceed Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Aishwarya R <aisr@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 14 Jul 2025 14:05:43 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 2/7] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL:HOSTAPD: Add DSCP Capability
 advertisement support

Introduce support for advertising DSCP policy capabilities in Beacon,
Probe Response, and (Re)Association Response frames. This is controlled
by a new configuration option enable_dscp_policy_capa.

When enabled, the AP includes a vendor-specific element indicating
support for DSCP policy and unsolicited DSCP policy capabilities, as
defined by the Wi-Fi Alliance.

Patch-dependency: none
Tag: DAP

Signed-off-by: Aishwarya R <aisr@qti.qualcomm.com>
